I really appriciate that you guys listened to our complains. I really like all of his skins now instead of almost liking them! I really like the Grey WW skin now, though I would like if you would change Hyena WW&#039;s W animation from the glowing red Eyes to some Engine fire things. Because that would be sick! Anyways this shows that you listen to what the comunity wants, so thank you riot (if you ever read this).
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 
I feel that most posts I see complains about something they want or something that should be better or that Yasuo is too op. I don&#039;t think I&#039;ve ever seen a post that is thanking riot for their good work and for creating the game that we love and play.
